@TaxCalculator.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000

### Configure tax rules for Germany
POST {{TaxCalculator.API_HostAddress}}/api/tax/rules/DE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "taxItems": [
    { "type": "fixed", "name": "CommunityTax", "amount": 1500 },
    { "type": "fixed", "name": "RadioTax", "amount": 500 },
    { "type": "flatRate", "name": "PensionTax", "rate": 0.20 },
    { "type": "progressive", "name": "IncomeTax", "intervals": [
      { "threshold": 10000, "rate": 0.00 },
      { "threshold": 30000, "rate": 0.20 },
      { "threshold": null, "rate": 0.40 }
    ]}
  ]
}

### Calculate tax for Germany
GET {{TaxCalculator.API_HostAddress}}/api/tax/DE?grossSalary=62000
Accept: application/json

### Calculate tax for unconfigured country
GET {{TaxCalculator.API_HostAddress}}/api/tax/XX?grossSalary=50000
Accept: application/json

###
